Name:		libglade2
Version:	2.6.4
Release:	9
Epoch:		1
License:	LGPL v2+
Group:		X11/Libraries
Source0:	http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/libglade/2.6/libglade-%{version}.tar.bz2
# Source0-md5:	d1776b40f4e166b5e9c107f1c8fe4139
